editorialSummary.text: Low-key counter-serve with American & Latin-American breads, pastries, sandwiches & empanadas.

originalText.text: This is a great small bakery. We had a delicious white chocolate, macadamia nut cookie and a meringue. Prices are reasonable. The person at that counter was friendly. I will definitely go back. The bakery has a good atmosphere.

originalText.text: Came all the way from Sweden to check this place out.  Lovely sweets and empanada.  The sweet rolls were far better than what Stockholm has to offer.  Sorry to have missed Jose.

originalText.text: Went a second time and as good as the first time! Got a few cookies and a mint watermelon lemonade that was divine! Great atmosphere, theming, and welcoming staff. I’m looking forward to my next trip to Big Booty Bakery!

originalText.text:
Echoing what everyone is saying about the customer experience. I was told WRONG information when it’ll be ready and the quoted price over the phone.
I ordered a two dozen cupcakes for an even  and was told they would be ready after 3pm. However, when I arrived at the bakery at 3:45, I was told they were running late because they didn’t know I was going to show up or not and the cupcakes wouldn't be ready for another 15 minutes(really? That’s unprofessional). I know they were busy so I came back after 30 minutes and still not ready. Had to wait another 20 minutes when they specifically told me it’ll be ready after 3.  It was incredibly frustrating as I had planned my day around picking up the cupcakes at the specified time.

To make matters worse, when I finally got the cupcakes, they were flat and looked nothing like the pictures on their website. Not only were they unappetizing in appearance, but they also tasted stale and too wet. I was shocked and disappointed that I had paid so much money for such poor quality cupcakes.

That wasn’t the end of it. To add insult to injury, when I went to pay for the cupcakes, I was charged more than the quoted price. The staff gave me some vague explanation about "oh he told you the wrong price," but I felt like I was being taken advantage of.

Overall, I had a terrible experience at this bakery and would not recommend it to anyone. The cupcakes were a total letdown and the customer service was unprofessional. Save yourself the trouble and go somewhere else for your baked goods.

originalText.text:
Big Booty Bread Co. is an absolute gem in the world of artisanal baking, and let me tell you, it's a slice of heaven in every bite! From the moment you step through the door, you're greeted by the warm, comforting aroma of freshly baked bread that instantly puts a smile on your face.

First and foremost, let's talk about the bread. Each loaf is a masterpiece, boasting a perfect crust and a soft, fluffy interior that's an absolute delight to sink your teeth into. Whether you're a fan of classic sourdough, hearty whole grain, or flavorful specialty loaves, Big Booty Bread Co. has something to satisfy every craving. And let's not forget their mouthwatering assortment of pastries and sweet treats! The croissants are flaky and buttery, the cinnamon rolls are pure bliss, and the cookies are downright addictive.

The dedication to quality and craftsmanship is evident in every aspect of the bakery. The ingredients are top-notch, the recipes are carefully curated, and the attention to detail is unparalleled. It's clear that the team at Big Booty Bread Co. pours their heart and soul into every batch they create, and the results speak for themselves.

Beyond the exceptional baked goods, the customer experience at Big Booty Bread Co. is simply wonderful. The staff is friendly, knowledgeable, and always ready with a smile. Whether you're a regular or a first-time visitor, you're treated like family from the moment you walk in. The inviting ambiance and charming decor only add to the overall appeal, making it a joy to linger over a cup of coffee and a pastry or to simply pop in for a quick pick-me-up.

In a world where fast food and mass-produced goods often dominate the culinary landscape, Big Booty Bread Co. stands out as a beacon of authenticity and passion. It's a place where tradition meets innovation, where every bite tells a story, and where the simple pleasure of good bread is celebrated in all its glory.

So, if you're craving a genuine, soul-satisfying bakery experience, do yourself a favor and pay a visit to Big Booty Bread Co. You'll not only leave with a bag full of delectable treats, but you'll also carry with you the warmth and joy that comes from supporting a truly exceptional small business.
